metadata.name: Flow
metadata.description:
"Creativity is nothing but mind set free." - Torrie T.

Nothing but Creative Flow :-)

I created this artwork on my iPad and made it after in 3D for this NFT. 

The one who gets this NFT (send me a proof) will receive a 50x70cm print on a Canson Montval 300g paper of the 2D version.
